.DT
load_player
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
load_player

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
load_player -  This method will load in the player file.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int load_player(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name to try and read in
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the player file exists, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/player_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will load in the player file.  It will return 0 if the player
file either does not exist or the input string is incorrect.
.EP

